---
import BlockOffLayout from '../../layouts/BlockOffLayout.astro';
---

<BlockOffLayout
  title="Returns & Refunds | Block OFF"
  description="Block OFF refund policy, 30-day money-back guarantee, and refund request instructions for founding creators."
  canonicalPath="/blockoff/returns"
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <header class="page-nav">
      <a class="brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
      <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation"><a href="/blockoff/#product">Product</a><a href="/blockoff/#how">How it works</a><a href="/blockoff/#dashboard">Dashboard</a><a href="/blockoff/#pricing">Pricing</a></nav>
    </header>

    <section class="page-hero bo-refund-hero">
      <span class="section-kicker">Returns & Refunds</span>
      <h1>A simple 30-day money-back guarantee.</h1>
      <p>If Block OFF is not the right fit, founding creators can request a refund within 30 days of purchase. No interrogation, no drama.</p>
      <button class="button primary" type="button" data-open-refund>Get refund</button>
    </section>

    <article class="legal-card bo-refund-policy">
      <section>
        <h2>30-day money-back guarantee</h2>
        <p>Founding creator purchases include a 30-day, no-questions-asked money-back guarantee. The 30-day window begins on the date your payment is completed through Dodo Payments.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>How refunds work</h2>
        <p>Submit a refund request from this page using the same email used at checkout. We review requests and issue eligible refunds within 24 hours after review. Your bank or card provider may take additional time to show the money back in your account.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>What is eligible</h2>
        <p>Early access purchases are eligible for a refund if the request is submitted within 30 days of purchase. If a payment provider, card network, or anti-fraud rule requires additional review, the refund may take longer to complete.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>After refund</h2>
        <p>After a refund is approved, paid access may be removed from the account. Connected YouTube or Instagram accounts can be disconnected, and you can request deletion of account data through support.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>For refund questions, contact <a href="mailto:support@blockoff.app">support@blockoff.app</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <div class="modal-backdrop" data-refund-modal hidden>
    <section class="waitlist-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="refund-title">
      <button class="modal-close" type="button" data-close-refund aria-label="Close refund form">x</button>
      <span class="section-kicker">Refund request</span>
      <h2 id="refund-title">Request your refund.</h2>
      <p>Sign in with the account used for Block OFF. We will verify your purchase automatically.</p>
      <form class="waitlist-form" data-refund-form>
        <p class="bo-refund-account" data-refund-account>Checking your account...</p>
        <label>
          <span>Reason for leaving</span>
          <select name="reason" required>
            <option value="">Select a reason</option>
            <option>It did not solve my comment problem</option>
            <option>I do not need it right now</option>
            <option>Setup was confusing</option>
            <option>Too expensive for me right now</option>
            <option>I bought it by mistake</option>
            <option>Other</option>
          </select>
        </label>
        <label>
          <span>Tell me your experience</span>
          <textarea name="experience" rows="5" placeholder="What happened? What should we improve?"></textarea>
        </label>
        <button class="button primary" type="submit">Submit refund request</button>
        <p class="form-status" data-refund-status role="status"></p>
      </form>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="modal-backdrop" data-refund-success hidden>
    <section class="waitlist-modal bo-refund-success" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="refund-success-title">
      <button class="modal-close" type="button" data-close-refund-success aria-label="Close confirmation">x</button>
      <span class="section-kicker">Request received</span>
      <h2 id="refund-success-title">Your refund request is submitted.</h2>
      <p>You’ll receive an update within 24 hours after review. Thanks for trying Block OFF.</p>
      <button class="button primary" type="button" data-close-refund-success>Done</button>
    </section>
  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a class="brand footer-brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
    <nav aria-label="Footer navigation">
      <a href="/blockoff/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/terms">Terms & Conditions</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/returns">Returns & Refunds</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/about">About Us</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/contact">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/support">Support</a>
      <a href="/blockoff/changelog">Changelog</a>
    </nav>
  </footer>

  <script src="../../scripts/blockoff-refund.js"></script>
</BlockOffLayout>
